{"tid":1055722,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"成日冇原因咁喊係咪有depression","createTime":"2019-03-10T17:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T21:54:11.000Z","uid":221993,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5f579da6607e23b51a738f8f2253ba20e896abe2","tid":1055722,"uid":221993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:22:49.000Z","msg":"成日冇啦啦喊，喊成半個鐘都有。做咩都冇乜心機，覺得自己做咩都唔好，好差。又有諗自殺。有睇開精神稿醫生，但唔知點開口&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f02807f42d1b3bd00c648a5517907516a03ccfd","tid":1055722,"uid":50900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:23:52.000Z","msg":"有冇好朋友可以傾下計"},{"pid":"c97118ec03bb03b2299598ea370155cb8350e8e4","tid":1055722,"uid":195975,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:24:57.000Z","msg":"相信你心中一定非常痛苦，才會如此寫下你的心聲！雖然，我並未完全了解你，但我明白置身痛苦中是怎樣一回事。有些人在困苦之中，會選擇放棄自己，不知道你是否也有這自殺的念頭？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你是否想過放棄自己，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡。因為人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=NaAPOzxPFgptGlwmNixMN6jD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=d1945c50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"be29984f9061458499e3deda2a03bd780cd3de99","tid":1055722,"uid":85024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:25:19.000Z","msg":"要睇持續幾耐<br />\n<br />\n有冇其他徵狀"},{"pid":"718ed7003b77db315fd1f95d9e0a69004a85c4ac","tid":1055722,"uid":221993,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1f02807f42d1b3bd00c648a5517907516a03ccfd","tid":1055722,"uid":50900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:23:52.000Z","msg":"有冇好朋友可以傾下計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:27:28.000Z","msg":"喺朋友身邊嘅開心果，冇一個可以放負<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ace9c36d21dd44f51a4bb032b97f109c1bf79e5","tid":1055722,"uid":221993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"be29984f9061458499e3deda2a03bd780cd3de99","tid":1055722,"uid":85024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:25:19.000Z","msg":"要睇持續幾耐<br />\n<br />\n有冇其他徵狀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:29:24.000Z","msg":"好耐&hellip;差唔多2年都會好sudden唔開心同想死。但最近係無啦啦坐咗喺度喊&hellip;同頻密咗"},{"pid":"3e7138c430348f17dd902942161943b966913770","tid":1055722,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:29:59.000Z","msg":"瞓教吧"},{"pid":"1174b7ccd3f6f23edcf148293a99433d0578e481","tid":1055722,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f579da6607e23b51a738f8f2253ba20e896abe2","tid":1055722,"uid":221993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:22:49.000Z","msg":"成日冇啦啦喊，喊成半個鐘都有。做咩都冇乜心機，覺得自己做咩都唔好，好差。又有諗自殺。有睇開精神稿醫生，但唔知點開口&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:30:45.000Z","msg":"有睇開精神科醫生？"},{"pid":"ac6620be55ba63ae13880ee6fa5d1f5463268260","tid":1055722,"uid":221993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3e7138c430348f17dd902942161943b966913770","tid":1055722,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:29:59.000Z","msg":"瞓教吧"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:31:29.000Z","msg":"瞓到嘅，我點會唔瞓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c34466ca8c84604b43d371b2ebbef94df9c679","tid":1055722,"uid":221993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1174b7ccd3f6f23edcf148293a99433d0578e481","tid":1055722,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f579da6607e23b51a738f8